<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Trendora</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #D10024;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/7oTcLHs.png" alt="Trendora Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Welcome to Trendora!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>Thank you for registering with Trendora! We're excited to have you join our community of shoppers.</p>

    <p>To complete your registration and verify your email address, please click the button below:</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
    </div>

    <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>

    <p><a href="<%= verificationUrl %>"><%= verificationUrl %></a></p>

    <p>At Trendora, you'll find:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The latest fashion trends</li>
      <li>High-quality products</li>
      <li>Competitive prices</li>
      <li>Excellent customer service</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our customer support team at support@trendora.com.</p>

    <p>Happy shopping!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Trendora Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2023 Trendora. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to you because you registered on our website. If you didn't register, please ignore this email.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
